hlight22\uc2 corporate social\b0 \highlight\uc2 -\b \highlight22\uc2 responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  policies, case studies giving practical examples of its work, its in-house corporate-responsibility committee, and investment-performance data that values the firm's portfolio at GBP 6 billion, or more than $11 billion.\par \par \uc2 Ben Harding, spokesman for international buyout firm \uc2 Apax Partners\uc2 , said 3i presented a model to aspire to in terms of the detail it provided concerning \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  -- the measure of a firm's consideration for its employees, the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  and society at large.\par \par \uc2 But the move is unlikely to be welcomed by all members of the industry. Some have criticized the increasing amount of information about corporate responsibility available to the general public as excessive.\par \par \uc2 In November last year, \uc2 Alchemy Partners\uc2  founder Jon Moulton labeled the increased levels of disclosure expected from private-equity firms as "mildly nuisancesome" and was critical of the moves being made by buyout groups toward disclosure akin to that of public companies.\par \par \uc2 In its 2008 report on \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , 3i said it had embarked on a three-year program last year to achieve carbon neutrality -- the act of neutralizing its carbon emissions through reduction and offset schemes -- by 2010.\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.djreprints.com/link/DJRFactiva.html?FACTIVA=weco20080822000091"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 License this article from Dow Jones Reprint Service}}}\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\cl