 record-breaking online fundraising campaign is using its high-profile presidential platform to pursue political clients overseas, corporate clients and institutions such as university alumni associations.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Blue State Digital's tools and consulting services have helped the Obama campaign raise more than $440m (\u163\'00\'A3251m) online from more than 2.5m donors, promoted 150,000 campaign events and provided a "virtual phone bank" to encourage supporters to call 2m potential voters.\par \par \uc2 It now plans to re-open an office in London in January, where it ran the online campaign for Ken Livingstone's unsuccessful bid to remain mayor this year, and has begun work with the Labour party and trades unions interested in mobilising their membership.\par \par \uc2 "We are fortunate in having a high-profile client right now named Barack," Thomas Gensemer, a former venture capitalist who worked on Howard Dean's internet campaign during the Democratic primaries four years ago, told the Financial Times.\par \par \uc2 Blue State Digital's work on the Obama campaign "has paid off, but the margins on other lines of business are much better," he admitted, as he set out the group's diversification plans.\par \par \uc2 Corporate clients in the US, such as a coalition of telecommunications groups, the Sundance Film Festival and Stonyfield Farms, an organic yoghurt brand, have helped raise non-political revenues to 50 per cent of the total, Mr Gensemer said.\par \par \uc2 However, it is now targeting a rapid international expansion, having signed clients in New Zealand and two other markets.\par \par \uc2 It is also pursuing a large group of institutions, from schools to churches, which have to date relied on direct mail for their fundraising and communication with members. "There are 4,000 major universities in the US. That alone is almost a separate business," Mr Gensemer said.\par \par \uc2 Corporate clients had so far shown few signs of cutting back on the \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  campaigns for which many have begun to use internet campaigning tools, he said, but still needed to adapt to certain aspects of the online \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 . "They have to be willing to give up a little bit of control," he said, pointing to the risks many companies saw in allowing users to upload content to their sites.\par \par \uc2 Blue State's work for Obama was "a campaign like no other", Mr Gensemer admitted. "Not everyone is going to raise half a billion dollars. It's not an ATM machine."\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RF\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 ftnewspaper_20081008.xml|20081008L126.487\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjust